(Auto Clock Out Plan \(Final Policy\)) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Policy Lock:) Tj
T* (- For every employee, max continuous session is 12 hours from clock_in.) Tj
T* (- If employee clocks out manually before 12 hours, keep existing normal flow.) Tj
T* (- If employee forgets clock_out, system auto-clocks-out exactly at clock_in + 12h.) Tj
T* (- After auto clock out, next clock-in should start a new session normally.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Implementation Workflow \(According to current codebase\):) Tj
T* (1\) Attendance API \(app/api/attendance/route.ts\)) Tj
T* (   - Add helper to close stale open record at 12h threshold.) Tj
T* (   - Trigger helper before handling new clock_in requests.) Tj
T* (   - Keep existing lock + duplicate guard unchanged.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (2\) Auto close details) Tj
T* (   - Find latest open session where clock_out IS NULL for employee.) Tj
T* (   - Compute auto_cutoff = clock_in + INTERVAL 12 HOUR.) Tj
T* (   - If now >= auto_cutoff, update:) Tj
T* (       clock_out = auto_cutoff) Tj
T* (       total_hours = 12.00) Tj
T* (       clock_out_source = auto_12h \(recommended metadata\)) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (3\) Manual flow compatibility) Tj
T* (   - If employee clocks out before 12h, use existing POST clock_out flow.) Tj
T* (   - No behavior change for normal shift completion.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (4\) Attendance Summary UI \(app/attendance-summary/page.tsx\)) Tj
T* (   - Continue showing clock_out if present.) Tj
T* (   - Add Auto badge when clock_out_source == auto_12h.) Tj
T* (   - Running status only for truly open \(not auto-closed\) sessions.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (5\) Historical backfill \(one-time\)) Tj
T* (   - For old open records, set clock_out = clock_in + 12h.) Tj
T* (   - Set total_hours = 12.00 and optional source metadata.) Tj
T* (   - Run as preview SELECT first, then safe UPDATE.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (6\) Validation checklist) Tj
T* (   - 13h later new clock_in: old session auto-closes, new session opens.) Tj
T* (   - Before 12h new clock_in attempt: blocked as already clocked in.) Tj
T* (   - Summary shows clock_out time and Auto badge for auto-closed rows.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Requested Improvements Included:) Tj
T* (- Shift-end+3h rule removed; hard overall 12h rule applied.) Tj
T* (- Existing normal/manual behavior preserved.) Tj
T* (- Continuous unattended 12h sessions are automatically closed.) Tj
ET
